  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine pleural level of procalcitonin in differents
      situations of pleuritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Determine pleural level of procalcitonin in pleuritis. Two periods First period evaluation in
      vitro study/ Determine adequat technique included type of samples tubes for adequat analysis.

      Second periods : Patient with pleuritis . Empyema or not
    </textblock>
